<article id="what-were-doing"  class="background-black paragraph-container" >

    <div  class="grid_wrapper full-video-with-text">

        <div class="grid_wrap">

            <div class="full-video-with-text__text">
                  <h3>What we’re doing</h3><p>Over the 60 years we’ve been around we’ve seen the devastating impact that climate change is having on our one shared home.</p><div><p>It can feel overwhelming, but by working as part of a global network with people, governments and business across the world, we’ve also seen that there’s hope.</p><p>Together, we can create a better future for people, nature and wildlife.</p><p><a class="btn 2" href="#what-can-i-do-title">I want to help</a></p></div>

            </div>

            <div class="full-video-with-text__video">
                <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-square">
  
