  <section id="what-can-i-do-title" class="paragraph paragraph--text paragraph-container paragraph-134271">
  <div class="article_wrapper">
    
      <center>
<h2>How you can help</h2>
</center>


  </div>
</section>

  


















 



   <section id="contribute-to-the-climate-recovery-fund" class="why_matter content-paragraph paragraph-container">
    <div class="species_image ">
        <picture >
                <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/content_slide_image/public/2023-07/Climate-Recovery-Fund_1.jpg?h=1e66e246&amp;itok=0ic23ygj" width="1000" height="600" alt="Climate Recovery Fund" class="image-style-content-slide-image" />




        </picture>

                <div class="copyright--image">© Michel Gunther / WWF-UK</div>
            </div>
    <div class="content content--padded species_image_contain">
            <h3>

<div class="field field--display_title">
  <h2>Contribute to the climate recovery fund</h2>
</div>
</h3>
            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p lang="EN-GB">Researchers say there’s now a 66% chance we will pass the 1.5C global warming threshold in the next five years. This could be catastrophic for our wildlife, our climate and all of us.</p>
<p lang="EN-GB">But there is still hope for our world, if we take the right action, right now, we can address its effects and give our natural world the chance to recover.</p>


      </div>
              

          <div class="btn-wrap">
                          
                   

     <div class="btn-wrap--item">
     <a href="https://support.wwf.org.uk/climate-recovery-fund?pc=AWJ014003&amp;ds_rl=1262365"  class="btn anchor_link  btn--white" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - https://support.wwf.org.uk/climate-recovery-fund?pc=AWJ014003&amp;ds_rl=1262365" ga-event-label=" Contribute to the climate recovery fund  Donate now">
         Donate now
     </a>
     </div>

     
     
      
     </div>
          </div>
</section>


  


















 



