        </picture>

                <div class="copyright--image">© WWF-UK</div>
            </div>
    <div class="content content--padded content_reverse">
            <h3>

<div class="field field--display_title">
  <h2>Download the My Footprint App</h2>
</div>
</h3>
            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p>Our everyday choices can collectively add up to help fight climate change. The My Footprint app gives you practical advice on how you can introduce positive changes to your life through a variety of challenges for you to take part in.</p>


      </div>
              

